<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./report.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Health Report</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3 border-bottom">
        <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center text-dark text-decoration-none">
            <span class="fs-4 ms-2">CareAId</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Home</a>
    </header>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">AI-Generated Health Report</h1>
        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Summary</h2>
                <p class="card-text"><% if (symptoms){%>
                    <%=symptoms%>
                <%}else{%>
                   Error
                <% } %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Analysis</h3>
                        <p>Our AI suggests that your symptoms might indicate the following conditions:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Condition 1:</strong> Mild dehydration</li>
                            <li><strong>Condition 2:</strong> Viral infection</li>
                            <li><strong>Condition 3:</strong> Seasonal allergies</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><em>Please consult a healthcare professional for confirmation.</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Recommendations</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water.</li>
                            <li>Take over-the-counter antihistamines for allergies.</li>
                            <li>Monitor symptoms and visit a doctor if they persist.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">Next Steps</h3>
                <p>Here are trusted specialists near you:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Dr. Jane Doe - General Physician (2 km away)</li>
                    <li>Dr. John Smith - ENT Specialist (3.5 km away)</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#book-appointment" class="btn btn-primary">Book an Appointment</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
            <button class="btn btn-success">Download Report</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center py-3 border-top">
        <p>&copy; 2024 CareAId. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
